OL,5, An Aberdeen mother and her young son   
OL,6, have died in a fire in India.          
OL,8,FDr Glory Valthaty, 43, and Joshua,     
OL,9,Feight, were believed to be visiting    
OL,10,Frelatives when the blaze broke out in a
OL,11,Fflat in Mumbai on Monday morning.      
OL,13,FDr Valthaty's husband and daughter were
OL,14,Funderstood to have also been on the    
OL,15,Fholiday.                               
OL,17,FJoshua was a pupil at Aberdeen's       
OL,18,FKaimhill School, whose headteacher     
OL,19,FSusie Webster said he had been a       
OL,20,Fmuch-loved member of his class.        
